<subSubSection pageId="75" pageNumber="133" type="discussion">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Matschie" authorityYear="1899" box="[725,884,676,705]" class="Mammalia" family="Pteropodidae" genus="Styloctenium" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="75" pageNumber="133" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Styloctenium</taxonomicName>
is sister to other living flying foxes in genera 
<taxonomicName box="[974,1091,711,744]" class="Mammalia" family="Pteropodidae" genus="Acerodon" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="75" pageNumber="133" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Acerodon</taxonomicName>
